      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a functional, reliable option for those on a budget. The exterior shows noticeable signs of use, including several paint chips, some minor dings, and visible scratches on the bumpers. Inside, the upholstery shows moderate wear and some fading, though it remains intact and smoke-free. Mechanically, the car runs and drives well, though it may require some minor maintenance or cosmetic attention in the near future to bring it up to a higher standard.",
