    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is an exemplary specimen in showroom condition. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved, exhibiting no signs of wear and maintaining its original factory luster. Every component has been rigorously inspected to ensure it meets the highest standards of mechanical and aesthetic excellence. For the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection, this represents a rare opportunity to acquire a truly peerless automobile.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
